      • Appointment

        public Appointment(int appointmentID,
                   java.lang.String title,
                   java.lang.String description,
                   java.lang.String location,
                   java.lang.String type,
                   java.time.Instant start,
                   java.time.Instant end,
                   java.lang.String username,
                   java.lang.String contact,
                   int customerID,
                   int userID,
                   int contactID)
        Class constructor. Stores appointment start/end times in the time zone set by the user OS. Displayed in UTC format.
        Parameters:
        appointmentID - the appointment ID
        title - the appointment title
        description - the appointment description
        location - the appointment location
        type - the appointment type
        start - the appointment start date and time in UTC
        end - the appointment end date and time in UTC
        username - the username of the user that created the appointment
        contact - the company contact associated with the appointment
        customerID - the customer ID for the appointment
        userID - the ID of the current user.
        contactID - the contact ID of the company contact associated with the appointment
